rden>{{cite web | url=https://www.meinhardt.net/news/the-garden-yangons-latest-mage-project-is-to-commence-construction/ | title=The Garden, Yangon\u2019s latest mega project, is to commence construction | date=2019-03-28 | publisher=Meinhardt }}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Infinity Condominium]]\n| \n| [[Yangon]]\n| ~{{convert|100.5|m|ft|0|abbr=on}}\n| 28\n| 2021\n| \n| <ref name=emporis-ygn-1/>\n|-\n| [[Sea View Condominium|Sea View Condominium III]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" | \n| rowspan=\"2\" | [[Myeik]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" | ?\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 28\n| rowspan=\"2\" | \n| rowspan=\"2\" | Phase 1 (2x22, 2x28) of the overall 12-building complex <br/> Phase 2 (8x32) not yet started\n| rowspan=\"2\" | <ref name=sea-view>{{cite news | url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gNqvlUuNhVA | title=Myeik Sea View Condo Phase 1 Launched | publisher=Eleven Broadcasting | date=2018-01-11 | language=Burmese | accessdate=2020-04-11}}</ref><ref name=cqhp-sv>{{cite web | url=https://www.cqhp.org/project/sea-view-condominium/ | title=Sea View Condominium | accessdate=2020-04-16 | publisher=CQHP Myanmar}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Sea View Condominium|Sea View Condominium IV]]\n|-\n| [[The Central, Yangon|The Central]]\n| \n| [[Yangon]]\n| ?\n| 27\n| 2020\n| Kaba Aye Pagoda Road\n| <ref name=mt-20200211>{{cite journal | author=Yi-Ywe Myint | url=https://www.mmtimes.com/news/metros-top-picks-yangon-housing-projects.html | title=Metro\u2019s top picks of Yangon housing projects | work=The Myanmar Times | date=2020-02-11}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[68 Residence]]\n| \n| [[Yangon]]\n| ~{{convert|93|m|ft|0|abbr=on}}\n| 26\n| 2020\n| At Saya San and Kaba Aye Pagoda Roads\n| <ref name=mt-20200211/>\n|-\n| [[Peninsula Residences]]\n| \n| [[Yangon]]\n| ~{{convert|93|m|ft|0|abbr=on}}\n| 26\n| \n| \n| <ref name=mt-2018-peninsula>{{cite journal | author=Yi-Ywe Myint | url=https://www.mmtimes.com/news/sales-peninsula-residences-yangon-commence-month.html | title=Sales at Peninsula Residences Yangon to commence this month | work=The Myanmar Ti